Amanita Design Privacy Policy for Games Distributed on Apple Arcade Subscription Service
We do not collect, process or store any personal data from any of our games.
Our games collect non-personal data using integrated Apple services for achievements, leaderboards and cloud saves such as Apple iCloud and Gamecenter. Such data are stored in these Apple services. We do not store personal or gameplay data on our servers. These services have their own privacy policies.
Our games collect, use, and disclose non-personal data from underage users in the same way as for other users, as described in this policy. Use of underage users’ data is limited to support internal operations of the game. Parents can learn more about how we handle data by contacting us at email address below.
We don’t use any in-app purchases and we don’t place any advertisements in our games.
Amanita Design s.r.o., Vrchlickeho sad 6, Brno, Czech Republic
Data privacy officer: Tomas Dvorak privacy@amanita-design.net